edu.arizona.biosemantics.semanticmarkup.ling.chunk

Class Chunk

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.arizona.biosemantics.semanticmarkup.ling.chunk.Chunk
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AbstractParseTree

    public class Chunk
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Cloneable
    A Chunk has a ChunkType, contains a ordered set of children chunks and may have properties. A AbstractParseTree constitutes a terminal Chunk.
    Author:
    rodenhausen
